@startuml sequence_calculate_zakat
' Sequence Diagram - Calculate Zakat
' Purpose: Shows the business workflow for starting a zakat calculation (draft),
' adding or linking items, recalculating, and finalizing. The ZakatService coordinates
' with RuleEngine and persistence. Actor: Accountant. Academic documentation.

title Sequence Diagram - Calculate Zakat

actor "Accountant" as User
participant "ZakatPage" as Page
participant "Zakat API" as API
participant "ZakatService" as Service
participant "RuleEngine" as RuleEngine
database "DB" as DB

== Start or resume draft ==
User -> Page : Start calculation (or open draft)
Page -> API : POST /zakat/calculation/start\nBearer company_token
API -> Service : start_calculation(company_id)
Service -> DB : Find or create DRAFT ZakatCalculation
Service -> DB : Auto-link unlinked FinancialItems to calculation
Service -> Service : recalculate_calculation(calculation_id)
Service -> RuleEngine : Apply rules to items
RuleEngine --> Service : Per-item results
Service -> DB : Persist ZakatItemResult, update zakat_base, zakat_amount
Service --> API : ZakatCalculation
API --> Page : CalculationResponse (items, rules_used, zakat_base, zakat_amount)
Page --> User : Show calculation summary

== Add or link items (optional) ==
User -> Page : Add item / Link existing item / Remove item
Page -> API : POST .../item or .../link-item or DELETE .../item
API -> Service : add_or_update_item / link_existing_item / remove_item_from_calculation
Service -> DB : Update FinancialItem or ZakatItemResult
Service -> Service : recalculate_calculation
Service -> RuleEngine : Apply rules
RuleEngine --> Service : Results
Service -> DB : Persist
Service --> API : CalculationResponse
API --> Page : Updated response
Page --> User : Update summary

== Recalculate (optional) ==
User -> Page : Recalculate
Page -> API : POST .../recalculate
API -> Service : recalculate_calculation(calculation_id)
Service -> RuleEngine : Apply rules
RuleEngine --> Service : Results
Service -> DB : Update ZakatCalculation, ZakatItemResult
Service --> API : CalculationResponse
API --> Page : Updated response

== Finalize ==
User -> Page : Finalize calculation
Page -> API : POST .../finalize
API -> Service : finalize_calculation(calculation_id)
Service -> DB : Set status=FINALIZED, calculation_date=now
Service --> API : ZakatCalculation
API --> Page : CalculationResponse
Page --> User : Show finalized result

@enduml
